==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Superpartient
<hw>Su`per*par"tient</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>superpartiens</ets>; <ets>super</ets> over + <ets>partiens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>partire</ets> to divide.]</ety> <fld>(Math.)</fld> <def>Of or pertaining to a ratio when the excess of the greater term over the less is more than a unit, as that of 3 to 5, or 7 to 10.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>  <rj><au>Hutton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Superphosphate</ent>⟦br⟧
